source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_00<tab>Osment at Crescent Cove is vexed by litter in the area.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_00<tab>クレセントコーヴのオスメントはちらかったゴミを前に途方にくれている。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_01<tab>A merchant from Limsa Lominsa has left rubbish scattered about the docks. Clean it up as a service to the distressed Osment.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_01<tab>リムサ・ロミンサから来た商人がゴミをそのまま置いていったようだ。桟橋に散らばっているゴミを片付けよう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_02<tab>You have finished cleaning up the rubbish that littered the docks. Speak to Osment once more.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_02<tab>ゴミを全て片付けた。「クレセントコーヴ」の「オスメント」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_03<tab>Though cleanliness has been restored, Osment is already lamenting the next Lominsan sloth who will darken his docks.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_SEQ_03<tab>桟橋は綺麗になったが、オスメントのやる気はまだまだ出そうにないようだ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_TODO_00<tab>Clean up the rubbish on the docks.
TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_000<tab>Ugggh, what a pain in the bloody arse. Who do those Lominsans think they are, anyway?
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_000はあ……面倒くせえ……。
あ～あ、もう何もする気がおきねえよ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_001<tab>Just look at all this, would you? A merchant from Limsa Lominsa dumped this junk when he shipped out. Claimed it wasn't fit for sellin', so he just up and left it!
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_001見てくれ、この荷物。
リムサ・ロミンサから来た商人が、置いていったんだ。
売り物なんかじゃねえよ、全部腐っちまったゴミさ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_002<tab>Barbarians! What passes for etiquette across the Strait of Merlthor?
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_002ったく、自分たちの土地じゃねぇからって、
ほったらかしにしやがって……。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_003<tab>Don't suppose I could ask you to clean up the rest for me, eh? Please? I've picked up so much junk already, the mere sight of it fair makes me gag.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_003あんた、俺の代わりにゴミを片付けてくれねえか？
俺はもうやりたくねえんだよ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_010<tab>Thank you, friend. Seeing this place clean again does my spirit good.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_010さっぱりしたら少しやる気が出てきたかな。
うん、ありがとよ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_011<tab>Though, I suppose some other Lominsan merchant will be by before long and leave more filth behind. <sigh> I hate my life.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL093_00342_OSMENT_011でもまたすぐに新しい積荷が来るんだろうなあ。
あ～あ、めんどくせえ……やる気が失せていくぜ。
